com.interpss.simu.multicase
Interface StudyCase

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
AclfStudyCase, ContingencyCase, DStabStudyCase
All Known Implementing Classes:
AclfStudyCaseImpl, ContingencyCaseImpl, DStabStudyCaseImpl, StudyCaseImpl
public interface StudyCase
extends NameTag

A representation of the model object 'Study Case'. Class for defining study case. Study case is intended for carrying a network model in serialized form, possibly being sent to a remote node or another thread for running analysis, such as Loadflow. The analysis result is then saved to the result object. Study case after the analysis with result might be sent to another node for further anlaysis, for example, Security Margin analysis. The modification could be applied before the analysis.

The following features are supported:

  • Case Number
  • Grid Node Id
  • Net Model String
  • Remote Return Status
  • Remote Return Message
  • Parent
  • Modification
  • Result

See Also:
MulticasePackage.getStudyCase()
